OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledge to fight for
OL,4,C'economic fairness for Wales' in
OL,5,Cmanifesto
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru says it will commit to
OL,8,Ffighting for a fair deal for Wales
OL,9,Fahead of their election manifesto
OL,10,Flaunch on Thursday morning.
OL,12,FThe party is expected to announce
OL,13,Fplans to secure more investment from
OL,14,FWestminster and to "protect and
OL,15,Fstrengthen devolution".
OL,17,FPlaid, which had four seats in the
OL,18,FParliament before the General Election
OL,19,Fwas called, is fighting in all 32
OL,20,Fconstituencies across Wales.
