OL,4,C'economic fairness for Wales' in
OL,5,Cmanifesto
OL,7,FRhun ap Iorwerth, the party's leader,
OL,8,Fsaid: "What sets Plaid Cymru apart is
OL,9,Fa record of not taking Wales for
OL,10,Fgranted and always putting the
OL,11,Finterests of our communities and
OL,12,Fnation first.
OL,14,F"This election is about one thing `
OL,15,Fthe economy."
OL,17,FHS2 Funding
OL,19,FAt the top of Plaid's list is securing
OL,20,Fmoney from the HS2 high-speed rail
OL,21,Fproject.
