OL,7,FThe rail link is currently classified
OL,8,Fas an 'England and Wales' project
OL,9,Fbecause the UK Government argue that
OL,10,Fthe line will benefit people in Wales.
OL,12,FHowever Plaid Cymru argue that the
OL,13,Fscheme only benefits people living in
OL,14,FEngland, and says Wales is entitled to
OL,15,Fbillions of pounds from Westminster
OL,16,Funder the Barnett Formula.
