OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledge to fight for
OL,4,C'economic fairness for Wales' in
OL,5,Cmanifesto
OL,7,FRhun ap Iorwerth said: "We will fight
OL,8,Fevery day for the billions owed to
OL,9,FWales from the HS2 high-speed rail
OL,10,Fproject, and for a fair funding model
OL,11,Fwhich funds our country according to
OL,12,Fneed, not population."
OL,14,FHe says his party will fight to secure
OL,15,F#4billion from the UK Government,
OL,16,Fwhich can be reinvested in public
OL,17,Fservices and "better reward our
OL,18,Fworkforce."
