OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledge to fight for
OL,4,C'economic fairness for Wales' in
OL,5,Cmanifesto
OL,7,FMr ap Iorwerth says the party will
OL,8,Fdemand a "fair funding system for
OL,9,FWales, based around our needs".
OL,11,FThe manifesto is expected to outline
OL,12,Fthe party's calls for funding
OL,13,FWestminster which would give the Welsh
OL,14,FParliament the power to make more
OL,15,Fdecisions about what happens here.
OL,17,FThe party leader said: "We will
OL,18,Faddress the cost-of-living crisis and
OL,19,Fprovide Welsh solutions to Welsh
OL,20,Fproblems."
