OL,4,C'economic fairness for Wales' in
OL,5,Cmanifesto
OL,7,FHe added: "For Wales, 14 years of Tory
OL,8,Fcuts and chaos have cut our public
OL,9,Fservices to the bone but there is no
OL,10,Fsign that a Labour government will
OL,11,Foffer any meaningful change either.
OL,13,F"Our communities have been left to pay
OL,14,Fthe price of decades of
OL,15,Funderinvestment from both London
OL,16,Fparties."
