OL,7,FThe manifesto, which is set to be
OL,8,Funveiled in Cardiff on Thursday
OL,9,Fmorning, will also outline how Plaid
OL,10,FCymru plans to redress what they
OL,11,Fdescribe as "economic unfairness".
OL,13,FThis includes plans the party have
OL,14,Falready outlined, including increasing
OL,15,Fwindfall taxes and devolving the Crown
OL,16,FEstate.
