OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledge to fight for
OL,4,C'economic fairness for Wales' in
OL,5,Cmanifesto
OL,7,FThe Crown Estate is the property
OL,8,Fportfolio which belongs to the King.
OL,9,FAll the money it makes goes directly
OL,10,Fto the UK Treasury. Plaid want to see
OL,11,Fthe money made from the estate in
OL,12,FWales go instead directly to the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment.
OL,15,F"Plaid Cymru will fight for economic
OL,16,Ffairness by increasing windfall taxes
OL,17,Fand demanding the transfer of powers
OL,18,Fover the Crown Estate to create green
OL,19,Fjobs and build prosperity," said Rhun
OL,20,Fap Iorwerth.
